WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 9=

01:43.980 --> 01:49.380
(Shuozhou)

01:50.430 --> 01:51.380
What's going on?

01:54.320 --> 01:55.220
Come on.

01:55.220 --> 01:56.060
Let's go take a look.

01:56.580 --> 01:57.910
They're opening the city gate.

01:59.860 --> 02:01.000
It hasn't opened in ages.

02:01.000 --> 02:01.860
Exactly.

02:01.860 --> 02:03.040
What happened?

02:03.040 --> 02:04.870
What could be so urgent?

02:07.700 --> 02:08.670
Is something wrong?

02:10.040 --> 02:10.700
Li.

02:10.710 --> 02:11.950
They're opening the city gate?

02:11.950 --> 02:12.820
It's open.

02:12.820 --> 02:14.180
The gate is really open.

02:14.180 --> 02:15.230
It's open.

02:20.390 --> 02:21.740
- The General.
- General!

02:53.740 --> 02:55.140
I have the head of Awo'erqi,

02:56.790 --> 02:59.300
the Hulan Force leader.

02:59.300 --> 03:00.460
We won the battle.

03:00.460 --> 03:01.700
Long live Great Liang!

03:02.070 --> 03:03.900
- Long live Great Liang!
- General!

03:04.270 --> 03:05.860
General, you're amazing!

03:05.860 --> 03:07.990
You're amazing!

03:08.350 --> 03:10.230
General, you're amazing!

03:11.180 --> 03:13.900
General!

03:14.460 --> 03:15.990
General, you're amazing!

03:16.270 --> 03:18.230
You're amazing!

03:18.230 --> 03:20.620
General, you're amazing!

03:22.210 --> 03:24.090
You're amazing!

03:24.460 --> 03:26.070
Long live Great Liang!

03:26.620 --> 03:28.110
Long live our nation!

03:28.830 --> 03:30.230
Long live Great Liang!

03:31.180 --> 03:33.390
Long live our nation!

03:33.390 --> 03:34.740
Long live Great Liang!

03:35.190 --> 03:36.700
Long live our nation!

03:38.020 --> 03:39.550
(I had always wondered)

03:40.180 --> 03:41.620
(why the Deliverance)

03:41.620 --> 03:42.990
(chose Duan Xu as its master.)

03:44.420 --> 03:45.460
(At this moment,)

03:46.180 --> 03:47.670
(I know the answer at last.)

03:48.580 --> 03:51.180
(He has no spirit power.)

03:51.790 --> 03:53.270
(His strong fate,)

03:53.420 --> 03:54.830
(heaven-blessed talent,)

03:55.550 --> 03:57.580
(and unordinary resolve)

03:58.420 --> 03:59.580
(aren't why)

03:59.580 --> 04:00.700
(the Deliverance chose him.)

04:02.550 --> 04:04.180
(This sword, born of mercy,)

04:04.670 --> 04:06.830
(can take lives and save them.)

04:07.460 --> 04:09.390
(It came into his hands)

04:09.830 --> 04:11.180
(because it wished to redeem him.)

04:11.550 --> 04:13.070
(That is why it made him its master:)

04:15.420 --> 04:17.150
(It's to cleanse the blood on his hands)

04:17.860 --> 04:19.380
(and the hardships etched on him.)

04:20.380 --> 04:21.420
Great news from Shuozhou.

04:21.910 --> 04:23.300
Awo'erqi is dead.

04:23.740 --> 04:24.990
The Chong Army has been routed.

04:25.470 --> 04:26.310
Tabai

04:26.590 --> 04:28.380
has successfully held Shuozhou City.

04:28.940 --> 04:31.590
Great news for the New Year.

04:31.940 --> 04:33.110
Great Liang prospers.

04:33.470 --> 04:35.110
Heaven bless Great Liang.

04:35.260 --> 04:36.790
Your Majesty, congratulations.

04:37.380 --> 04:38.350
Your Majesty,

04:38.740 --> 04:40.550
now that Awo'erqi is dead,

04:40.820 --> 04:42.150
the one he strongly backed,

04:42.150 --> 04:44.180
the 13th Prince, rose up.

04:44.710 --> 04:46.730
The 6th Prince recalled
the Fenglai Force as well,

04:47.060 --> 04:48.220
claiming to rescue the throne,

04:48.470 --> 04:49.740
but truly to seize power.

04:50.260 --> 04:51.470
Chong Court is now

04:51.470 --> 04:52.710
in complete turmoil,

04:52.820 --> 04:54.100
with no mind for anything else.

04:54.260 --> 04:55.350
Once Fenglai pulls back,

04:55.710 --> 04:57.820
Qin Huanda can soon

04:58.300 --> 04:59.470
reclaim Yuzhou.

04:59.790 --> 05:00.830
In the battle of Shuozhou,

05:00.910 --> 05:01.750
Duan Xu's merit

05:02.420 --> 05:03.420
was beyond measure.

05:04.260 --> 05:05.100
Your Majesty,

05:05.820 --> 05:07.260
Shuozhou is stable for now.

05:07.590 --> 05:09.300
But the food shortage remains.

05:09.500 --> 05:10.990
Sending provisions is urgent.

05:11.420 --> 05:12.260
Your Majesty,

05:12.550 --> 05:14.350
the provisions are all prepared.

05:14.990 --> 05:16.150
The enemy has withdrawn.

05:16.500 --> 05:17.910
Now is the best time to send them.

05:19.110 --> 05:19.950
Very good.

05:20.380 --> 05:22.790
Fang, handle this matter.

05:23.420 --> 05:24.860
Yes, Your Majesty.

05:35.470 --> 05:36.340
Physician, you...

05:36.340 --> 05:37.190
Dress the wounds.

05:37.990 --> 05:39.550
The General has many wounds.

05:39.860 --> 05:40.990
His robes must be removed

05:41.000 --> 05:42.060
before he can be treated.

05:42.060 --> 05:43.670
That's easy. I'll do it.

05:44.910 --> 05:46.060
You're a girl.

05:46.060 --> 05:46.900
Move aside.

05:47.030 --> 05:47.870
I'll do it.

05:49.380 --> 05:50.780
- General.
- He…

06:02.180 --> 06:03.790
Miss He, please

06:05.180 --> 06:06.380
dress my wound.

06:15.820 --> 06:16.860
I know a little medicine.

06:17.710 --> 06:19.500
Let me bandage the General.

06:20.710 --> 06:21.590
My thanks, Miss.

06:23.550 --> 06:24.990
Why can she do it, but not me?

06:26.400 --> 06:27.330
You may hurt him.

06:27.330 --> 06:28.910
- The General fears pain.
- I...

06:28.910 --> 06:29.750
Let's step outside.

06:29.990 --> 06:30.860
Let the General rest.

06:31.180 --> 06:32.130
Yes, you should go.

06:32.140 --> 06:33.230
I'll stay with the General.

06:33.230 --> 06:34.120
Your voice is too loud.

06:34.120 --> 06:35.120
The General needs quiet.

06:35.130 --> 06:35.830
Come on.

06:36.300 --> 06:37.620
Since when am I loud? I...

06:39.590 --> 06:41.060
What do you know? This...

06:42.230 --> 06:43.110
Enough, enough.

06:43.110 --> 06:43.950
Don't pull me.

06:55.260 --> 06:56.710
If it hurts, just cry out.

06:57.180 --> 06:58.150
If your throat aches,

06:58.350 --> 06:59.650
you may forget the pain you bear.

07:03.030 --> 07:04.300
You're quite careless.

07:06.180 --> 07:07.590
So, you truly feel nothing.

07:12.790 --> 07:13.770
Shall I ask Captain Meng

07:13.790 --> 07:14.550
to take my place?

07:15.380 --> 07:16.220
Perfect.

07:16.350 --> 07:17.620
Then you can explain to her

07:18.150 --> 07:19.310
how the other wounds on you

07:19.320 --> 07:19.950
came to be.

07:27.710 --> 07:29.380
To have you bandage my wounds

07:30.710 --> 07:31.670
is a great honor for me.

07:32.790 --> 07:34.260
Since you are my spell bearer,

07:35.060 --> 07:36.030
I will not let you perish

07:36.030 --> 07:36.870
so easily.

07:38.990 --> 07:39.910
Aside from the stab

07:39.910 --> 07:40.860
in Rib Fifteen,

07:41.420 --> 07:42.940
the other wounds aren't too deep.

07:44.550 --> 07:46.260
Thank you for your care.

07:46.710 --> 07:47.990
Then recover as soon as you can.

07:48.220 --> 07:49.220
Fulfill our pact with me.

07:49.620 --> 07:50.710
Then please,

07:51.860 --> 07:53.010
be a little gentler with me.

07:58.990 --> 07:59.940
You asked me

07:59.940 --> 08:00.910
to dress your wound.

08:00.910 --> 08:02.030
And you're so picky.

08:02.420 --> 08:04.180
Do you take me for a servant?

08:06.670 --> 08:08.260
How would I be picky with you?

08:09.590 --> 08:10.710
I'm begging you.

08:16.910 --> 08:18.150
Since you know it hurts,

08:19.060 --> 08:20.990
why risk yourself like that?

08:26.910 --> 08:27.750
Back then,

08:29.150 --> 08:30.940
Tabai was not yet mine.

08:34.990 --> 08:35.900
But now,

08:37.350 --> 08:38.310
the Tabai Army

08:39.310 --> 08:41.020
is finally yours.

08:52.380 --> 08:54.100
(Yueran Fragrance)

08:54.110 --> 08:54.950
Miss Duan,

08:56.230 --> 08:57.070
your sachet.

09:04.380 --> 09:05.310
It has agarwood,

09:05.620 --> 09:06.460
amber,

09:06.740 --> 09:08.260
storax, mint leaves,

09:08.470 --> 09:09.950
Bletilla, and benzoin in it.

09:10.350 --> 09:11.430
The finest-grade scents.

09:12.590 --> 09:13.430
Very nice.

09:13.900 --> 09:14.740
In all of Nandu,

09:14.950 --> 09:16.660
none surpasses your craft.

09:17.470 --> 09:18.590
You flatter me, Miss Duan.

09:19.230 --> 09:20.190
By the way, Miss Duan,

09:20.190 --> 09:21.310
I recall you once told me

09:21.540 --> 09:23.140
this was for Young Master Xu.

09:23.780 --> 09:25.140
Could he have returned to Nandu?

09:27.110 --> 09:27.950
Not yet.

09:28.110 --> 09:29.260
It's for the Spring Festival.

09:29.430 --> 09:30.660
If I forget him,

09:30.950 --> 09:31.990
he'll be upset with me.

09:33.620 --> 09:35.190
I only pray he turns peril to peace

09:35.860 --> 09:37.710
and fulfills his long-held wish,

09:39.110 --> 09:40.070
so he can come back soon

09:41.310 --> 09:42.350
to reunite with us.

09:43.940 --> 09:46.020
(Yueran Fragrance)

09:46.020 --> 09:46.860
I have an umbrella.

09:46.860 --> 09:47.860
Let's go home.

09:47.860 --> 09:48.830
Move, move!

09:48.830 --> 09:49.780
Quick, quick!

09:50.190 --> 09:51.380
Sorry, coming through.

09:51.390 --> 09:52.270
Make way, make way!

09:52.270 --> 09:53.140
Go, go!

09:53.140 --> 09:54.650
Milady, wait here for me.

09:54.660 --> 09:55.890
I'll fetch the carriage driver.

09:56.590 --> 09:57.430
Be careful.

09:59.780 --> 10:00.740
Wipe over there.

10:01.210 --> 10:02.350
Come here to avoid the rain.

10:02.370 --> 10:02.910
Come here.

10:03.830 --> 10:05.110
This rain came out of nowhere.

10:14.620 --> 10:15.460
Excuse me.

10:24.260 --> 10:27.380
(Tabai Army, Duan Xu)

10:34.740 --> 10:36.070
The Censorial Counselor,

10:36.070 --> 10:36.910
Fang Xianye?

10:37.260 --> 10:38.350
After Nandu got the news,

10:38.590 --> 10:40.100
it sent provisions to Shuozhou at once.

10:40.540 --> 10:41.540
I just did not expect

10:42.020 --> 10:43.310
Mr. Fang to lead the convoy.

10:45.590 --> 10:46.860
One report for Marshal Qin,

10:47.190 --> 10:48.180
one letter for my family.

10:49.140 --> 10:50.260
Please send them out for me.

10:50.430 --> 10:51.270
Yes.

10:53.190 --> 10:54.430
No matter who brings the grain,

10:55.190 --> 10:56.480
it eases the army and the people.

10:57.500 --> 10:58.660
Why do you look so troubled?

10:58.900 --> 11:00.160
I don't think Fang Xianye comes

11:00.620 --> 11:01.710
with good intent.

11:02.350 --> 11:03.230
Is everything ready

11:03.430 --> 11:04.350
for the provisions?

11:04.590 --> 11:05.430
Everything is set.

11:06.780 --> 11:07.660
Good.

11:07.660 --> 11:08.660
Pass the order down.

11:09.190 --> 11:10.030
We leave tonight.

11:11.990 --> 11:12.830
Young Master,

11:12.990 --> 11:13.860
we're delivering grain

11:13.860 --> 11:14.780
to Duan Xu

11:14.780 --> 11:16.110
under Chancellor Du.

11:16.380 --> 11:17.540
Must we rush so hard?

11:17.860 --> 11:18.950
There's a clear order.

11:19.350 --> 11:20.190
The grain delivery

11:20.620 --> 11:21.460
must not be delayed.

11:22.260 --> 11:23.500
We're already here.

11:24.660 --> 11:25.620
Let's wait and see.

11:26.780 --> 11:27.620
Yes.

11:31.900 --> 11:32.910
Captain Han, what's wrong?

11:33.710 --> 11:34.590
General,

11:34.590 --> 11:35.430
word has just come.

11:35.990 --> 11:37.430
Marshal Qin will be here soon.

11:40.990 --> 11:42.190
Marshal Qin is coming.

11:43.500 --> 11:44.380
I'm feeling unwell.

11:45.070 --> 11:46.190
Have Commandant Wu

11:46.740 --> 11:47.830
receive him.

11:48.710 --> 11:49.550
Yes.

11:50.780 --> 11:51.620
Captain Han,

11:57.020 --> 11:58.500
any more questions?

12:10.540 --> 12:11.380
No.

12:12.110 --> 12:13.110
I only know

12:13.800 --> 12:14.840
that I'm now Han Lingqiu,

12:14.850 --> 12:16.070
Captain of Tabai Army.

12:17.260 --> 12:18.350
I do not wish to pursue

12:19.500 --> 12:20.430
what happened before.

12:50.860 --> 12:52.590
You've recovered well.

12:52.590 --> 12:54.350
You even made the trip to camp.

12:56.900 --> 12:58.620
Even if the commander is badly hurt,

12:59.430 --> 13:01.140
they should still visit the camp

13:01.900 --> 13:02.780
to steady the troops.

13:04.380 --> 13:05.860
Thanks for checking on me.

13:06.780 --> 13:08.110
I only came to see

13:08.310 --> 13:09.170
when you can begin

13:09.180 --> 13:10.260
honoring our agreement.

13:10.780 --> 13:11.950
If it's okay with you,

13:13.020 --> 13:13.860
any time.

13:15.860 --> 13:17.310
You're back rather late today.

13:22.230 --> 13:23.530
I once made a promise to someone.

13:24.070 --> 13:25.190
After Shuozhou was relieved,

13:25.500 --> 13:26.830
I would grant him one question.

13:29.190 --> 13:30.190
Today, he came to see me.

13:31.330 --> 13:32.420
I was prepared to answer

13:32.430 --> 13:33.430
all his questions.

13:34.540 --> 13:35.780
But he seemed not to care.

13:43.260 --> 13:44.100
Han Lingqiu?

13:45.660 --> 13:46.830
We were in the same grade.

13:48.070 --> 13:49.500
We barely talked.

13:51.260 --> 13:52.500
We crossed paths most

13:53.990 --> 13:55.150
during the Blindfolded Trial.

13:57.140 --> 13:59.460
(Trial)
The contest was cruel.

14:00.110 --> 14:01.070
Only one would be given

14:01.860 --> 14:02.820
a codename to graduate.

14:03.860 --> 14:04.700
At that time,

14:05.660 --> 14:07.110
only Han and I were left.

14:09.470 --> 14:10.710
He'd be defeated,

14:12.590 --> 14:14.260
only later than the others.

14:22.620 --> 14:23.660
I left that long scar

14:23.660 --> 14:24.500
across his face.

14:27.230 --> 14:28.310
When you'd kill him?

14:29.740 --> 14:30.580
No.

14:31.310 --> 14:32.470
I never meant to kill him.

14:33.190 --> 14:34.070
I wanted to save him.

14:35.070 --> 14:36.860
When I looked into his eyes,

14:36.860 --> 14:38.350
I saw my own reflection there.

14:39.600 --> 14:41.120
So, I used a small ruse

14:41.540 --> 14:43.160
to make him seem dead.

14:45.140 --> 14:47.090
I made him drink a decoction
to erase his memory,

14:48.310 --> 14:50.280
swapped him with a corpse
bearing the same wound,

14:51.020 --> 14:52.020
and sent him out.

14:59.780 --> 15:01.020
Do you want to hear my story?

15:05.110 --> 15:06.500
Last time, when I had my hand

15:06.500 --> 15:07.860
around your throat to end you,

15:08.350 --> 15:09.860
you would not say a word.

15:10.350 --> 15:11.710
And now you are willing to speak?

15:12.500 --> 15:13.620
When you meant

15:13.620 --> 15:14.540
to end me,

15:15.830 --> 15:17.110
of course, I'd say nothing.

15:18.710 --> 15:20.350
But when I reached out to you,

15:22.780 --> 15:23.830
you took my hand.

15:28.070 --> 15:29.120
Then I knew I could say it.

15:31.190 --> 15:32.620
In this vast world,

15:33.310 --> 15:34.830
life in the All-Knowing

15:35.590 --> 15:37.110
was far better than begging.

15:38.380 --> 15:39.680
We never lacked food or clothes,

15:40.110 --> 15:41.130
and the Priest would read

15:41.140 --> 15:42.370
from the Aphorisms of Cangshen.

15:43.140 --> 15:44.430
Mentor favored me greatly.

15:44.950 --> 15:46.070
He taught me martial arts

15:46.860 --> 15:47.920
and guided me in strategy.

15:49.830 --> 15:50.990
For the first few months,

15:50.990 --> 15:51.830
I was happy.

15:53.310 --> 15:54.310
But after a few months,

15:55.190 --> 15:56.620
our real training finally began.

15:58.470 --> 15:59.310
Or rather,

15:59.710 --> 16:01.190
our game of survival began.

16:03.740 --> 16:05.190
Chong laws were strict.

16:06.140 --> 16:07.620
My mentor oversaw the code.

16:08.310 --> 16:10.010
The People of Liang
were punished at will.

16:10.380 --> 16:11.470
And our training

16:12.070 --> 16:13.840
was their chance to be free again.

16:15.160 --> 16:16.950
At first, we were all afraid.

16:17.310 --> 16:18.710
But soon we understood.

16:19.430 --> 16:20.270
There,

16:20.470 --> 16:21.660
one's kindness was

16:22.620 --> 16:24.350
the cruelest thing to themselves.

16:24.620 --> 16:25.460
Don't end me.

16:26.260 --> 16:27.350
Please, don't end me.

16:28.110 --> 16:29.470
Don't end me.

16:30.260 --> 16:31.140
Please.

16:31.740 --> 16:32.580
Don't end me.

16:35.010 --> 16:35.860
This went on

16:35.860 --> 16:36.990
for who knows how long.

16:38.150 --> 16:40.020
Until one day, as always,

16:41.130 --> 16:42.130
I went on a mission.

16:49.740 --> 16:50.900
The sunlight was harsh.

16:52.190 --> 16:53.030
That day,

16:53.590 --> 16:54.660
the weather was fair.

16:55.260 --> 16:56.590
The weather today

16:57.710 --> 16:58.740
is truly fine.

17:00.430 --> 17:01.270
Please show

17:02.430 --> 17:03.270
some mercy.

17:05.340 --> 17:06.430
This is someone alive

17:08.010 --> 17:10.710
in this world, like me.

17:11.670 --> 17:13.300
He, too, loves fair weather.

17:16.230 --> 17:17.340
That was when I realized

17:20.190 --> 17:21.470
I was becoming a monster.

17:23.190 --> 17:24.710
Again and again, I told myself:

17:25.020 --> 17:25.860
Stay awake.

17:26.250 --> 17:27.100
Do not kill me.

17:27.260 --> 17:28.430
Do not become a monster.

17:31.020 --> 17:32.710
One day, you will return to the light

17:33.540 --> 17:34.740
and reclaim your true name,

17:35.580 --> 17:37.470
living openly as an upright man.

17:39.390 --> 17:40.910
When I left the All-Knowing,

17:42.020 --> 17:43.020
I swore that one day

17:44.490 --> 17:46.280
I would end this madness.

17:52.150 --> 17:53.190
Then did you succeed?

17:54.390 --> 17:55.740
You're human,

17:55.740 --> 17:56.580
instead of a monster?

18:01.190 --> 18:02.390
I suppose.

18:05.630 --> 18:06.780
Just not quite a normal one.

18:16.630 --> 18:17.470
You've been

18:17.820 --> 18:19.300
treating yourself like an object,

18:20.470 --> 18:21.330
hammering and mending,

18:21.340 --> 18:22.630
patching yourself as you grew up.

18:24.540 --> 18:25.430
All these years,

18:25.630 --> 18:27.300
mired in such wretched muck,

18:28.540 --> 18:29.820
you did not turn crooked.

18:36.820 --> 18:38.020
What is normal?

18:38.870 --> 18:39.950
What is not?

18:41.870 --> 18:42.710
General,

18:43.630 --> 18:44.470
little fox,

18:45.470 --> 18:46.540
my spell bearer,

18:47.990 --> 18:49.020
live your life,

18:50.390 --> 18:51.990
finish your days in this world,

18:52.190 --> 18:53.340
fulfill your wishes,

18:54.340 --> 18:55.820
and die without worries.

18:56.990 --> 18:58.500
This is the most normal life.

19:14.910 --> 19:15.750
Yan,

19:16.100 --> 19:16.940
what brings you here?

19:17.630 --> 19:18.820
The Chong Army was routed,

19:18.820 --> 19:19.660
with heavy losses.

19:20.100 --> 19:21.570
Something's off with the Fusang Tree,

19:21.780 --> 19:22.670
so I came.

19:23.910 --> 19:25.150
You made the trip just for that?

19:26.740 --> 19:28.390
What did you bring this time?

19:28.670 --> 19:30.340
As expected, nothing gets past you.

19:38.230 --> 19:39.780
I had this painted by a mortal master.

19:40.580 --> 19:41.630
Through winter and spring,

19:41.780 --> 19:42.670
the steadfast spirit

19:43.920 --> 19:44.900
of pine and cypress

19:45.020 --> 19:46.020
never changes.

19:47.430 --> 19:48.820
As expected of a master.

19:50.190 --> 19:51.030
Do you like it?

19:57.020 --> 19:58.060
But lately,

19:58.060 --> 19:59.310
I prefer plum blossom.

19:59.920 --> 20:01.070
It braves the frost and snow,

20:01.300 --> 20:02.300
never yielding.

20:15.580 --> 20:16.630
Is it because

20:18.580 --> 20:19.870
of that mortal general?

20:24.260 --> 20:25.490
He was only a passing amusement

20:25.500 --> 20:26.300
on my rest day.

20:35.470 --> 20:36.670
Plum blossoms fade with ease.

20:37.540 --> 20:39.340
They're fleeting delight.

20:41.100 --> 20:42.950
But pine and cypress stay evergreen.

20:44.430 --> 20:46.060
I'll keep this painting for you.

20:47.120 --> 20:48.580
I won't disturb you any longer today.

20:48.820 --> 20:49.960
Get some proper rest first.

21:27.670 --> 21:29.500
I'm Duan Xu, the General!

21:29.910 --> 21:33.020
General, welcome back!

21:33.300 --> 21:34.100
Charge!

21:34.150 --> 21:34.990
Charge!

21:34.990 --> 21:37.820
(Shuozhou)

21:37.820 --> 21:41.300
Tabai is fierce as tigers!

21:43.990 --> 21:48.430
Tabai is fierce as tigers!

21:48.430 --> 21:49.990
Here, you are the General.

21:52.390 --> 21:53.870
Xiaoxiao, you're finally here.

21:55.190 --> 21:56.340
It is just one victory.

21:56.470 --> 21:57.500
Is it worth all this joy?

21:57.500 --> 21:58.710
This time is different.

21:58.710 --> 22:00.100
We beat the Chong people

22:00.300 --> 22:01.540
and drove them away.

22:01.540 --> 22:02.500
Shuozhou is safe now.

22:02.500 --> 22:03.780
How could we not be glad?

22:04.260 --> 22:05.470
You sound like an expert

22:05.470 --> 22:06.670
when it comes to war.

22:07.430 --> 22:08.780
Xiaoxiao, come with me.

22:08.780 --> 22:09.820
We can't be late.

22:09.980 --> 22:12.220
(Victory Cake)

22:12.230 --> 22:13.250
There is still some left.

22:15.500 --> 22:16.540
Two Victory Cakes, please.

22:16.540 --> 22:17.380
Coming right up.

22:18.150 --> 22:20.100
We've had it before, right?

22:20.390 --> 22:21.300
You want

22:21.300 --> 22:22.140
more again?

22:24.670 --> 22:25.550
No need, Xiaoxiao.

22:25.550 --> 22:26.740
I have money now. I'll pay.

22:27.300 --> 22:28.710
Where did you get it?

22:30.060 --> 22:31.340
I earned this myself.

22:31.770 --> 22:33.710
While you were with the General,

22:33.910 --> 22:34.870
I ran errands

22:34.870 --> 22:35.910
for Commandant Xia.

22:36.990 --> 22:38.150
You used to look after me.

22:38.150 --> 22:39.100
Now that I have money,

22:39.100 --> 22:39.940
I'll look after you.

22:40.430 --> 22:41.270
Here.

22:41.820 --> 22:42.660
You eat it.

22:46.580 --> 22:47.910
It's so sweet. Really tasty.

22:48.230 --> 22:49.230
Put it

22:50.100 --> 22:50.940
into your pouch.

22:51.680 --> 22:53.180
- Thanks.
- Food!

22:54.060 --> 22:55.020
Food from the court!

22:55.810 --> 22:57.190
- Food!
- Food!

22:57.190 --> 22:58.780
Hurry! Go look!

22:59.340 --> 23:00.580
The General must be distributing

23:00.600 --> 23:01.070
grain again.

23:01.710 --> 23:02.740
Take this basket.

23:11.870 --> 23:12.710
General,

23:13.100 --> 23:14.100
Censorial Counselor Fang

23:14.470 --> 23:15.310
has arrived.

23:18.260 --> 23:19.430
Have the officers and soldiers

23:19.870 --> 23:20.820
welcome him.

23:22.870 --> 23:23.790
Mr. Fang's grain convoy

23:23.810 --> 23:24.550
went around us

23:25.260 --> 23:26.340
and distributed grain.

23:30.670 --> 23:31.510
Everyone,

23:32.100 --> 23:34.340
I am Fang Xianye,

23:34.340 --> 23:35.180
Grain Commissioner.

23:35.740 --> 23:36.580
His Majesty

23:36.780 --> 23:38.870
ordered me to bring grain.

23:39.500 --> 23:40.710
Shuozhou has long been at war;

23:40.710 --> 23:41.780
provisions are running low.

23:41.910 --> 23:44.100
His Majesty cares for the people,

23:44.430 --> 23:45.500
so he procured grain.

23:46.060 --> 23:46.900
Now,

23:47.100 --> 23:48.540
the Tabai Army,

23:48.670 --> 23:50.030
under Marshal Qin Huanda's command,

23:50.090 --> 23:51.340
has returned in great victory.

23:51.630 --> 23:52.470
From this day on,

23:52.710 --> 23:54.500
with the soldiers here,

23:54.710 --> 23:56.580
you will have grain to eat

23:56.740 --> 23:57.580
and clothes to wear.

23:59.430 --> 24:00.270
Distribute the grain!

24:14.470 --> 24:15.310
It's grain!

24:15.540 --> 24:16.910
Real grain!

24:17.580 --> 24:19.260
Just days after the victory,

24:19.580 --> 24:21.670
grain from Nandu arrived.

24:22.910 --> 24:24.470
Thank you, my lord!

24:24.630 --> 24:25.630
Thank you!

24:25.630 --> 24:27.820
Thanks, my lord!

24:28.780 --> 24:30.580
Thank you, my lord!

24:31.260 --> 24:32.290
No need to rush.

24:32.300 --> 24:33.230
There's enough for all.

24:33.230 --> 24:34.070
Enough for everyone!

24:34.080 --> 24:35.150
Don't crowd. Easy now.

24:35.710 --> 24:37.060
Line up, everyone.

24:37.710 --> 24:38.580
Don't crowd.

24:41.670 --> 24:42.510
Easy now.

24:43.340 --> 24:44.230
Enough for everyone!

24:48.740 --> 24:49.670
You don't want some?

24:52.630 --> 24:54.430
He's so annoying.

24:56.150 --> 24:56.990
Why do you say that?

24:57.390 --> 24:58.710
It was the General

24:58.710 --> 24:59.710
who won the battle,

24:59.990 --> 25:01.670
so the grain could get through.

25:01.910 --> 25:02.750
But now,

25:02.760 --> 25:04.230
he won't mention the General

25:04.740 --> 25:05.860
and acts like he was the one

25:05.880 --> 25:07.340
who saved the whole city.

25:14.060 --> 25:15.020
General Duan,

25:16.500 --> 25:17.630
your prize has been claimed

25:18.670 --> 25:20.150
by someone else.

25:24.280 --> 25:25.190
Thank you, thank you.

25:32.060 --> 25:33.020
Line up over there.

25:33.520 --> 25:34.630
Hold it steady.

25:34.630 --> 25:35.920
When will it be my turn?

25:36.140 --> 25:36.990
I...

25:36.990 --> 25:38.100
We won the war,

25:38.300 --> 25:39.340
and now he wins hearts.

25:41.170 --> 25:42.010
Food for the people

25:42.020 --> 25:43.100
matters more than anything.

25:43.950 --> 25:44.990
Everyone gets a share.

25:57.540 --> 25:58.380
General Duan,

26:00.020 --> 26:01.030
I trust you've been well.

26:02.000 --> 26:02.850
Censorial Counselor,

26:02.870 --> 26:04.190
you came far to bring grain here.

26:05.340 --> 26:06.180
Thank you on behalf

26:06.740 --> 26:07.910
of Shuozhou's people.

26:07.910 --> 26:09.580
(Clear-sighted and Astute)

26:09.580 --> 26:10.950
You took Shuozhou by surprise

26:10.950 --> 26:11.950
and held the city.

26:11.950 --> 26:13.100
You're amazing.

26:13.710 --> 26:15.430
I came to ease your burden.

26:15.910 --> 26:17.260
So, you have another charge.

26:17.260 --> 26:18.940
(Upright and Incorruptible)

26:21.740 --> 26:22.870
The Ministry of Personnel

26:23.150 --> 26:24.100
has appointed me

26:24.100 --> 26:26.150
to take over all civil affairs.

26:33.260 --> 26:34.430
In that case,

26:34.950 --> 26:35.950
I will comply.

26:36.500 --> 26:37.430
If you take over here,

26:37.820 --> 26:38.820
what are we to do?

26:39.020 --> 26:39.860
Report!

26:43.100 --> 26:44.500
Marshal Qin has ordered

26:44.500 --> 26:45.950
Tabai to withdraw
outside the city

26:46.020 --> 26:47.020
and await further orders

26:47.020 --> 26:47.870
once he arrives.

26:47.880 --> 26:48.760
Outside the city?

26:49.950 --> 26:51.170
The spring chill still lingers.

26:51.190 --> 26:52.740
Making the soldiers camp outside now

26:52.740 --> 26:53.710
is too harsh.

26:53.990 --> 26:55.190
Are you behind this?

26:55.530 --> 26:56.930
How could it be such a coincidence?

26:56.990 --> 26:58.060
You just arrived,

26:58.190 --> 27:00.020
and Marshal Qin's order followed.

27:00.260 --> 27:01.100
How dare you!

27:01.470 --> 27:03.390
You struck without orders.

27:03.390 --> 27:04.470
That broke orders.

27:04.950 --> 27:06.670
Marshal Qin remembers

27:06.670 --> 27:07.670
the service you rendered

27:07.910 --> 27:09.190
and spares you punishment.

27:11.580 --> 27:12.470
Spares us?

27:12.710 --> 27:13.550
I...

27:20.340 --> 27:21.360
As Marshal Qin commanded.

27:26.430 --> 27:27.270
Mr. Fang,

27:28.870 --> 27:30.230
if we withdraw,

27:31.020 --> 27:32.910
and the Chong remnants rush in,

27:33.300 --> 27:34.580
we may not return in time.

27:35.150 --> 27:36.300
If chaos breaks out,

27:37.580 --> 27:38.670
it'd trouble you as well.

27:40.740 --> 27:42.500
You're right.

27:42.930 --> 27:43.780
The city's defenses

27:43.780 --> 27:44.950
are indeed vital.

27:45.740 --> 27:46.580
In that case,

27:46.820 --> 27:48.190
before Marshal Qin arrives,

27:48.390 --> 27:49.670
you should handle

27:49.820 --> 27:51.390
the city's defense duty.

27:53.540 --> 27:54.380
Then please,

27:55.190 --> 27:56.910
govern Shuozhou for Tabai.

28:03.420 --> 28:11.780
(Shuozhou Yamen)

28:11.780 --> 28:12.620
General,

28:13.710 --> 28:14.670
we just handed

28:14.670 --> 28:15.780
Shuozhou to Fang Xianye?

28:16.340 --> 28:17.230
General,

28:17.230 --> 28:18.470
what a mess.

28:18.670 --> 28:19.510
I mean, him...

28:20.390 --> 28:21.630
I just can't accept it.

28:21.990 --> 28:23.470
Should I let you

28:24.100 --> 28:24.940
govern Shuozhou?

28:25.820 --> 28:26.660
I...

28:26.910 --> 28:27.750
Forget it.

28:28.020 --> 28:29.060
That lad got off easy.

28:39.640 --> 28:40.480
Hurry up.

28:41.100 --> 28:42.710
Though that man is annoying,

28:43.670 --> 28:45.060
we still need to eat.

28:48.190 --> 28:49.030
Don't rush.

28:49.530 --> 28:50.390
Make way.

28:50.390 --> 28:51.230
Make way, thank you.

28:51.230 --> 28:52.070
Thank you.

28:52.800 --> 28:53.670
Give me more.

28:53.670 --> 28:54.630
Two in my family.

28:55.230 --> 28:56.070
Give me some.

28:56.300 --> 28:57.670
Thank you, thank you.

28:57.910 --> 28:59.710
Don't shove. Don't shove.

28:59.710 --> 29:00.580
Enough for everyone.

29:00.710 --> 29:01.550
Next.

29:03.020 --> 29:04.100
(Lin Mansion)

29:04.100 --> 29:05.020
This is wonderful.

29:05.550 --> 29:06.430
We can't be late.

29:06.430 --> 29:07.630
Yes, hurry.

29:07.820 --> 29:08.660
Xiaoxiao...

29:13.280 --> 29:14.150
That person

29:14.150 --> 29:15.340
looks like Xiaoxiao.

29:16.220 --> 29:17.630
Good thing we brought a big basket.

29:17.630 --> 29:18.470
We can get plenty.

29:24.710 --> 29:25.550
General!

29:25.710 --> 29:26.550
Xiaoxiao!

29:26.910 --> 29:27.750
Chenying,

29:28.470 --> 29:29.660
come tonight with your sister.

29:29.950 --> 29:30.790
We have grain now.

29:31.190 --> 29:32.710
The victory banquet will be a feast.

29:34.390 --> 29:36.190
For trifles like a victory banquet,

29:36.190 --> 29:37.300
is it worth having you

29:37.300 --> 29:38.340
handle it in person?

29:39.430 --> 29:40.270
Not me.

29:40.390 --> 29:41.610
Censorial Counselor Fang Xianye

29:41.620 --> 29:42.930
came to bestow imperial rewards.

29:43.190 --> 29:44.030
Why not?

29:45.870 --> 29:46.710
Fair enough.

29:46.870 --> 29:48.230
You can eat a little more.

29:55.260 --> 29:56.870
You sound like I'm a pet you raise,

29:58.190 --> 29:59.540
asking every day if I'm well

30:00.150 --> 30:00.990
or fat enough,

30:01.580 --> 30:02.810
so you can butcher and eat me.

30:04.430 --> 30:05.910
If you think you're ready,

30:06.580 --> 30:07.910
I could carve you up right now.

30:09.950 --> 30:10.790
Then,

30:11.430 --> 30:13.060
tonight,

30:14.100 --> 30:15.950
are we having pork

30:15.950 --> 30:17.470
or the General?

30:23.100 --> 30:23.950
General,

30:23.950 --> 30:25.050
does it mean that every time

30:25.070 --> 30:25.730
we win a battle,

30:25.730 --> 30:27.260
we get a victory banquet?

30:28.670 --> 30:30.340
He truly adores you now.

30:30.670 --> 30:31.780
He keeps saying

30:31.780 --> 30:33.630
he'll be a hero like you.

30:35.910 --> 30:37.230
You want to go to war with me?

30:38.470 --> 30:39.350
General,

30:39.360 --> 30:40.780
I want to fight on the field

30:40.910 --> 30:41.870
and defend our nation

30:41.870 --> 30:42.870
like you.

30:43.990 --> 30:44.830
Good.

30:45.740 --> 30:46.870
If you want to join the army,

30:47.220 --> 30:48.740
you can drill and train with me daily.

30:49.150 --> 30:49.990
Alright.

30:52.780 --> 30:53.620
But...

30:53.950 --> 30:54.790
General,

30:55.240 --> 30:56.730
if I go there,

30:56.870 --> 30:57.740
does that mean

30:57.750 --> 30:58.830
I won't see Xiaoxiao again?

31:05.950 --> 31:07.060
It doesn't matter.

31:07.870 --> 31:09.260
We'll part ways someday anyway.

31:12.870 --> 31:13.710
So,

31:16.260 --> 31:17.230
Xiaoxiao,

31:19.300 --> 31:20.630
you still don't want me,

31:20.630 --> 31:21.470
do you?

31:25.670 --> 31:26.510
Yes.

31:43.390 --> 31:44.230
Chenying.

31:44.580 --> 31:45.420
Chenying!

31:50.160 --> 31:51.470
Aren't you going to comfort him?

31:52.750 --> 31:53.740
Children cry for a while,

31:53.740 --> 31:54.630
and then they're fine.

31:55.580 --> 31:57.060
That day had to come.

31:58.190 --> 31:59.560
Why are you pushing Chenying away?

32:04.910 --> 32:05.820
No one can stay

32:05.820 --> 32:06.780
with someone forever.

32:08.430 --> 32:09.470
I care for Chenying

32:10.190 --> 32:11.030
only for a deal

32:11.030 --> 32:12.020
with his father.

32:12.950 --> 32:13.820
Once the deal is done,

32:13.820 --> 32:14.870
I will leave.

32:16.100 --> 32:17.050
It is the same with you.

32:18.020 --> 32:19.630
After I trade for your five senses,

32:20.100 --> 32:21.470
I'll return to where I came from.

32:23.670 --> 32:24.780
Can you bear it?

32:28.990 --> 32:30.780
Mortals' lives are short.

32:31.820 --> 32:33.500
General, mind your own path

32:33.760 --> 32:35.130
and recover soon to honor our pact.

33:24.470 --> 33:25.310
In a moment,

33:26.230 --> 33:28.630
if Fang Xianye dares come,

33:29.230 --> 33:30.260
I will send him out

33:30.540 --> 33:32.740
on a stretcher.

33:32.740 --> 33:34.100
- Your words?
- My words.

33:34.100 --> 33:34.950
We all heard it,

33:34.960 --> 33:35.790
Commandant Wu.

33:40.150 --> 33:40.990
General Duan,

33:41.540 --> 33:42.430
the Censorial Counselor

33:42.430 --> 33:43.630
is tied up with state affairs,

33:43.820 --> 33:44.710
so he could not come.

33:44.710 --> 33:46.470
He sent me with Nandu wine

33:46.670 --> 33:47.950
to honor the soldiers.

33:48.230 --> 33:49.230
He truly dared not come.

33:52.870 --> 33:53.870
Thank him for me.

33:54.740 --> 33:56.150
- Come on.
- Come on, brothers.

33:56.540 --> 33:57.660
We are in for a treat today.

33:57.710 --> 33:58.780
Enjoy!

34:05.020 --> 34:06.740
Fang Xianye knows his place.

34:08.580 --> 34:09.540
Listen up, brothers.

34:10.350 --> 34:11.190
This time,

34:11.950 --> 34:12.950
the General

34:13.390 --> 34:15.020
killed the Chong leader

34:15.580 --> 34:17.140
by his own strength alone.

34:17.910 --> 34:18.990
What an achievement!

34:19.500 --> 34:20.340
Today,

34:20.790 --> 34:22.140
it is

34:22.140 --> 34:23.350
Tabai's victory banquet;

34:23.700 --> 34:25.500
it's also the General's.

34:26.310 --> 34:27.150
Everyone,

34:27.830 --> 34:28.670
this cup of wine

34:29.500 --> 34:30.430
is to the General.

34:30.830 --> 34:32.390
To the General!

34:34.910 --> 34:35.790
May Great Liang

34:36.700 --> 34:37.950
soon reclaim the lost land

34:38.470 --> 34:39.390
and rise anew!

34:39.950 --> 34:42.950
May Great Liang soon reclaim

34:43.140 --> 34:44.500
the lost land and rise anew!

34:44.500 --> 34:45.340
Cheers!

34:56.220 --> 34:59.100
♪Beneath war-lit walls, axes break♪

34:59.100 --> 35:02.060
♪Gongs sound, spears rest,
and bones remain♪

35:02.270 --> 35:04.990
♪Homes lie like tombs, bare and still♪

35:05.220 --> 35:08.060
♪Graves guard the borderlands♪

35:08.060 --> 35:09.620
♪Heroic souls depart♪

35:09.750 --> 35:13.790
♪Willing to sleep through the ages♪

35:14.310 --> 35:15.580
♪I shall return with you♪

35:15.580 --> 35:19.180
♪With liquor on the far road♪

35:20.220 --> 35:21.750
♪Heroic souls depart♪

35:21.750 --> 35:25.430
♪Willing to sleep through the ages♪

35:26.270 --> 35:27.620
♪I shall return with you♪

35:27.750 --> 35:31.270
♪With liquor on the far road♪

35:32.180 --> 35:33.790
♪Heroic souls depart♪

35:33.790 --> 35:37.750
♪Willing to sleep through the ages♪

35:38.270 --> 35:39.830
♪I shall return with you♪

35:39.830 --> 35:43.540
♪With liquor on the far road♪

35:45.750 --> 35:46.590
Captain Meng.

35:46.990 --> 35:48.180
Come on. Have a drink with us.

35:48.180 --> 35:49.020
Captain Meng.

35:49.180 --> 35:50.060
Come on, bottoms up.

35:50.130 --> 35:50.990
Come on, come on.

35:50.990 --> 35:51.830
Here.

35:52.100 --> 35:53.500
Come, come. Fill it up.

35:55.580 --> 35:56.540
Drink it all.

35:56.540 --> 35:57.380
Well done.

35:59.540 --> 36:00.380
Meng Wan,

36:01.990 --> 36:03.350
I want...

36:06.620 --> 36:07.790
I want...

36:08.430 --> 36:09.350
To drink with me?

36:09.350 --> 36:10.470
You should've said so.

36:10.700 --> 36:11.540
Fill it up.

36:12.870 --> 36:13.710
Bottoms up.

36:26.430 --> 36:27.270
Xia Qingsheng?

36:28.870 --> 36:29.710
Xia Qingsheng!

36:30.910 --> 36:32.060
Wake up, Xia Qingsheng.

36:32.060 --> 36:32.900
Wake up.

36:34.220 --> 36:35.190
That's all you can drink?

36:52.830 --> 36:53.670
Captain Meng,

36:54.060 --> 36:55.580
Commandant Xia can't hold his liquor.

36:56.060 --> 36:57.100
- Let's drink.
- Sure.

36:57.100 --> 36:57.940
Come on.

37:00.140 --> 37:01.060
- Drink.
- Cheers.

37:01.060 --> 37:01.900
Come on.

37:25.540 --> 37:27.140
If you're free,

37:27.870 --> 37:28.870
could you change

37:31.140 --> 37:32.310
my dressing again?

37:35.580 --> 37:36.870
I've sat for hours.

37:37.830 --> 37:38.910
My wound is bleeding again.

37:39.830 --> 37:40.670
It hurts so much.

37:41.690 --> 37:43.470
Take my sense of touch now.

37:45.180 --> 37:46.100
Pain is a mortal's way

37:46.100 --> 37:47.180
of protecting themselves.

37:48.180 --> 37:49.180
If you felt no pain,

37:49.580 --> 37:50.990
the danger would only grow.

38:03.750 --> 38:05.270
When cutting through foes

38:05.580 --> 38:06.910
and facing Fifteen,

38:07.530 --> 38:09.270
you were like a spirit with no feeling.

38:10.020 --> 38:11.830
